bilingual.target: 很少有人能找到心甘情愿的投资者。
是做心甘情愿的几内亚猪意思

bilingual.source: Use of willing attitude, a happy-go-lucky life.
bilingual.target: 用心甘情愿的态度，过随遇而安的生活。

bilingual.source: Nothing is impossible to a willing mind, love included.
bilingual.target: 于一个心甘情愿的心,没有什么不可能; 爱也如此.

bilingual.source: Perhaps, love is willing to pay the share, close-knit.
bilingual.target: 或许，爱就是心甘情愿的付出，甘苦与共的分享。

bilingual.source: The best life is use of willing attitude, a happy-go-lucky life.
bilingual.target: 最好的生活是用心甘情愿的态度，偷偷撸欧美色图过随遇而安的生活。

bilingual.source: While you're objective, logical and willing to move forward as the week gets going, others may be more on the touchy -feely side.
bilingual.target: 在本周初，你制订的目标要客观符合逻辑，并且要心甘情愿的想在本周大干一番，也许身边其他的人会感情用事（但是你不能这样）。

bilingual.source: Some people became interested in, and more are willing to.
bilingual.target: 一些人对此产生了兴趣，更多人愿意。

bilingual.source: Why are some people willing to spend so much money on a tiny bottle of perfume?
bilingual.target: 为什么有些人愿意花这么多钱买一小瓶香水？

yingyinNormal.en: Willing to adopt triplets? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 想领养三胞胎吗？不！

yingyinNormal.en: I have always been willing to talk.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我一直很愿意与你磋商。

yingyinNormal.en: You're bluffing. Are you willing to risk it?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你只是在吓唬我。你真愿意冒这个险吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Colosseum has not been willing to back down so far.
yingyinNormal.zh: 克鲁斯曼是不会轻易妥协的。

yingyinNormal.en: Michael was willing to die for what he believed in.
yingyinNormal.zh: 迈克尔愿意为他的信念而死。

yingyinNormal.en: Sheldon, I'm really impressed you're willing to try this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢尔顿，我非常惊讶你居然愿意来亲身体验。

yingyinNormal.en: All yours if you're willing to reinstate the Roommate Agreement.
yingyinNormal.zh: 都是你的，只要你愿意恢复室友协议。

yingyinNormal.en: We are willing to continue discussions on a potential compromise.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们愿意继续谈判基于一个有可能性的妥协的基础上

yingyinNormal.en: And China is willing to help in any way we can.
yingyinNormal.zh: 中方愿在力所能及的范围内尽量帮忙。

yingyinNormal.en: Because knowing both sides of the coin, I really think that there is a love story willing to be told, willing to unfold.
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为我同时了解双方，所以我相信，两者之间有一个爱情故事将要讲述，将要展开。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. If we're willing to show that we are truly repentant.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是呀，我们可以证明真的悔改了。

yingyinNormal.en: There are some owners who are willing to forego the season.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有一些老板愿意走在这个赛季之前

yingyinNormal.en: What were they? What? The things you had to be willing to do?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你指什么事？什么？那些你不得不主动去做的事

yingyinNormal.en: And they're willing to pay extra to get that particular size onion.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们愿意付出额外的金钱。来得到那个完美大小的洋葱。

yingyinNormal.en: And if I'm the only one, then so be it. But I'm willing to bet I'm not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果我是唯一一个，那也没关系，但我相信，不会只有我一个。

yingyinNormal.en: We can celebrate the holidays, because they're willing to miss their own.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们能够庆祝这些节日因为他们愿意错过他们自己的度假。

yingyinNormal.en: Look, Steve. I'm willing to take the risk. And, this certainly qualifies.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你看，史蒂夫，我可以冒一些险，当然这是取得回报的代价。

yingyinNormal.en: You were so desperate for love. You were willing to marry me, just like that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你对爱情是如此的孤注一掷，你是那么希望嫁给我。

yingyinNormal.en: It's so weird you think he's so gross, yet you're willing to eat his crackers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真奇怪，你觉得他很恶心却又在吃他的饼干。

yingyinNormal.en: Maybe it can, if you are willing to guide it, to nurture it, to believe in it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 也许可以，只要你悉心指引他、培育他、相信它。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: The survey conducted by Harris Poll indicates that more Americans are <highlight>willing</highlight> to work in retirement.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 哈里斯民意调查机构进行的这项调查显示，更多的美国人愿意在退休后继续工作。

examination_example.sentence: As it turns out, many people are actually perfectly <highlight>willing</highlight> to talk—and may even be flattered to receive your attention.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 事实证明，许多人实际上非常愿意交谈，甚至可能会因为得到你的关注而受宠若惊。

examination_example.sentence: The majority were <highlight>willing</highlight> to cooperate with the tester in learning a new skill, demonstrating that they trusted his leadership.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 大多数孩子愿意与测试者合作学习一项新技能，这表明他们信任测试者的领导能力。
